content: I’m a passionate Data Science Enthusiast pursuing Masters in Business Analytics at University of Illinois at Chicago with specialization in Data Science. I’m working as a Teaching Assistant for Business Statistics for Information and Decision Sciences department. My academic interests include Natural Language Processing, Feature Engineering and Extraction.
